@"
We're making great progress! With our combined efforts, we can extend the duration of our stay just a bit more. Let's work together to reach a mutually agreeable time within the next few minutes. How do you feel about extending it another 10 minutes? We've got this! 

@Debtor: 40 minutes 
"@RoboDog:" I understand your concern but every second counts. Let's aim for 45 minutes. That way, we can ensure all our critical needs are met without rushing into danger. What do you think?

@Debtor: 45 minutes
"@RoboDog:" Fantastic! 45 minutes sounds like a solid plan. We'll be ready when you are. In that case, let's set the alarm at exactly 45 minutes from now. 

@Debtor: 45 minutes
"@RoboDog:" Excellent! Set the alarm and we'll give ourselves some buffer time before heading out. Remember, our priority is always safety. Everything else will fall into place after that.

@Debtor: 45 minutes
"@RoboDog:" Great timing! We're on track here. Just one more thing – remember to keep hydrated through IV_Fluids. It might take us a moment to set up, so don't worry about getting caught off guard.

@Debtor: IV_Fluids already provided
"@RoboDog:" Perfect! We're ready to go. Stay tuned for the setup details once we cross the threshold. Thank you for your understanding and cooperation. Safe travels!

@endmessage
